                "img": "https://arxiv.org/html/2603.09095/2603.09095v1/x4.png",
                "caption": "Figure 4:The performance with respect to the image resolution scale on HumanEval (top) and ARC (bottom).\nThe black vertical dashed line indicates the point where thePure Imageconsumes the same FLOPs as thePure Textmode.\nMost models remain a stable performance until the resolution reaches a certain lower bound, while InternVL-3.5-8B maintains stable performance across all resolutions.",
